{
  "stem": "10587.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But Funfteichen was already a little different.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They-- you-- the bunks were next to each other, but it was separate bunks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] first morning we got up-- first of all, the barracks were not ready.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we all slept on the floor the first night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because we helped to finish the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We built a concentration camp in Funfteichen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they brought people from Auschwitz and people from another forced labor camp, which was called Markstedt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's how we-- and so the barracks were not ready, so we were-- we were told to clean the barracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, where is the broom?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they said, the broom is on your hat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, he says, you stupid jerk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They give us like a round hat, you know, with the stripes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we used our hat to sweep the barracks out and to erect the bunks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the next day, they assigned us to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they called the arbeitskommandos, which was a little bit more orderly already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most people were assigned to-- to-- the Krupps factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was not that lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was assigned to work on-- build bridges, lay railroad tracks, dig ditches for sewer lines and-- and I worked for a company, Henckel and Zeiner, Henckel and Sons.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now they are very well known by their knives they manufacture, Henckel knives.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were-- at that time, that's what we were doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And many people died there, too, from the exposure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we worked winter time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was already getting cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we-- and so it was very, very cold, and we were wearing those pajama uniforms-- very thin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the only thing, really, that kept people alive, is maybe some were a little stronger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was younger.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, constantly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a kapo that was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a heavy-set guy, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I understand that he was a furniture mover, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to-- they called him the Schlepper, because they used to move furniture from one place to another without putting it on a truck.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would just move furniture all day long, would take a whole mattress and bath and whole-- and tie it up and schlep it over to a few-- maybe a half a mile away or so.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and he was a pretty rough guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was probably-- he worked very hard all his life, and he was probably very disappointed with society.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was getting even, you know, with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was rough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Many people, from the cold weather, from exposure to the cold, they were frost-bitten, and they were-- got sick.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And many-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] where I was, you know, because in the-- in the Krupps factory, you worked inside under a roof.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At least there was-- you were doing-- unless you're loading or unloading, but most of the time, you worked inside.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was always exposed to the elements.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If it was raining, we were soaking wet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If it was snowing, we-- it was freezing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So people were getting-- I-- I noticed the same situation as in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were getting-- first their feet would swell, and then their head would swell, and then they would just keel over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The food was-- we were given already a little-- a little more decent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was-- it seemed like there was like-- we were given a piece of bread in the morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at night, we were given a bowl of soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The soup was-- you could taste the sand, in other words.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It looked like-- seemed like they-- they never cooked it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- had potatoes that were not peeled and cabbage and whatever they threw in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but at least they had a place where you can sit down on benches and-- and a table.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and you can at least eat in a-- in a sub-human way, but a little more improved than Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sanitary conditions, they were always concerned, because they were already getting more closer, you see, with the kind of work, and also where the people were going to the Krupps factory.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were-- they had better sanitary conditions, where you can-- at least you could-- but everything was like a mass production.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were holes through-- the same kind of a concept.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at least you can take a shower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I never remember getting a-- ever getting another uniform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean-- so maybe-- I don't know-- but at least you could take a shower.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A constant.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a constant process of delousing.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
